title: Dashing
description: Don't want to spend your entire day waiting in a salon? Let Dashing come to you!
Brought to you by my project group, JB INC., Dashing is the online destination for bringing beauty & wellness professionals to their client's home - Beauty-on-Delivery.
Talented licensed freelance professionals can showcase their work and connect with new & exisiting clients, all while building their business.

title: ReReddit
description: ReReddit is my version of the popular Reddit site!
It uses an express backend and redux frontend, along with basic React/JavaScript.
Login and explore some posts - or add some! Also, comment on a post, or delete your comment; subscribe to a subreddit. See your list of subscribed subreddits in a dropdown list.
